# W3Scan - Advanced Reconnaissance Toolkit

[![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8%2B-blue)](https://www.python.org/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Issues](https://img.shields.io/badge/issues-report-red)](https://github.com/yourusername/w3scan/issues)

**W3Scan** adalah toolkit reconnaissance all-in-one yang dirancang untuk bug bounty hunter, penetration tester, dan security researcher. Tool ini menggabungkan subdomain enumeration, port scanning, directory bruteforce, WAF detection, subdomain takeover check, dan masih banyak lagi — dalam satu paket yang mudah digunakan.

## Fitur Utama

- **Subdomain Enumeration** cepat dengan brute-force + live check (title, status code, tech stack)
- **Port Scanning** akurat menggunakan `nmap` (top 1000 ports + service detection)
- **Directory & File Bruteforce** berkecepatan tinggi dengan `ffuf`
- **Subdomain Takeover Detection** (deteksi CNAME dangling)
- **WAF Detection** akurat dengan `wafw00f`
- **HTTPS/TLS Certificate Info**
- **Antarmuka GUI Modern** (Tkinter) dengan progress bar, stop button, dan real-time log
- **Fallback CLI** jika GUI tidak tersedia
- **Output JSON** terstruktur dan mudah dibaca
- **Multi-threading** untuk performa maksimal

## Struktur Project
w3scan/
├── w3scan_gui.py              # Antarmuka GUI utama (modern & user-friendly)
├── w3scan_advanced.py         # Core engine reconnaissance (versi powerful)
├── simple-domain-scanner.sh   # Script bash sederhana untuk quick scan
├── upgraded-domain-scanner.sh # Versi upgrade dari script bash
├── wordlists/                 # (Opsional) Tempat wordlist default
│   ├── subdomains.txt
│   └── directories.txt
├── results/                   # Folder hasil scan otomatis
└── README.md
text## Instalasi & Dependencies

### 1. Install Dependencies (wajib untuk performa terbaik)

```bash
# Go-based tools (super cepat & akurat)
go install -v github.com/projectdiscovery/dnsx/cmd/dnsx@latest
go install -v github.com/projectdiscovery/httpx/cmd/httpx@latest
go install -v github.com/ffuf/ffuf/v2@latest

# System tools
sudo apt update && sudo apt install nmap wafw00f -y    # Ubuntu/Debian
# brew install nmap wafw00f                            # macOS
# pacman -S nmap wafw00f                               # Arch Linux
Catatan: Pastikan $GOPATH/bin atau $HOME/go/bin ada di $PATH Anda.
2. Jalankan Tool
Menggunakan GUI (rekomendasi untuk pemula)
Bashpython3 w3scan_gui.py
Fitur GUI:

Input domain & wordlist mudah
Progress bar real-time
Tombol Stop Scan
Output JSON otomatis
Log berwarna dengan timestamp

Menggunakan CLI (versi powerful)
Bashpython3 w3scan_advanced.py --domain example.com --wordlist wordlists/subdomains.txt
Contoh lengkap:
Bashpython3 w3scan_advanced.py \
  --domain target.com \
  --wordlist wordlists/subdomains.txt \
  --output results/target_com_20251224.json
Quick Scan dengan Bash (tanpa Python)
Bashchmod +x upgraded-domain-scanner.sh
./upgraded-domain-scanner.sh example.com
Contoh Output
Hasil disimpan dalam format JSON yang rapi:
JSON{
  "target": "example.com",
  "timestamp": "2025-12-24 15:30:45",
  "ip": "93.184.216.34",
  "live_subdomains": [
    {
      "host": "www.example.com",
      "url": "https://www.example.com",
      "status": 200,
      "title": "Example Domain",
      "tech": ["Apache", "Ubuntu"]
    }
  ],
  "open_ports": [
    {"port": 80, "service": "http"},
    {"port": 443, "service": "https"}
  ],
  "takeover_vulnerable": [],
  "directories": [
    {"url": "https://example.com/admin/", "status": 403, "size": 277}
  ],
  "waf": "Cloudflare"
}
Wordlist Rekomendasi

Subdomain: https://github.com/danielmiessler/SecLists/blob/master/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt
Directory: https://github.com/danielmiessler/SecLists/blob/master/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt

